title: Cher sings to 'the world's loneliest elephant'
description: Kaavan the elephant had languished in a zoo in Pakistan for decades. But thanks to Cher and a social media campaign, he's on his way to a new home in Cambodia.

title: Trump admits 'it's hard to get to the Supreme Court'
description: CNN's Amara Walker and Carl Bernstein discuss President Trump's admission during a Fox News interview that "it's hard" to get cases to the Supreme Court and how Trump's continued legal challenges could undermine future election processes.

title: Jon Ossoff defends claim that GOP senator is a 'crook'
description: CNN's Dana Bash pushed back on Georgia Senate-challenger Jon Ossoff's claim that Sen. David Perdue (R-GA) is a "crook."

title: David Prowse, the original Darth Vader, dies aged 85
description: British actor David Prowse, who played Darth Vader in the original "Star Wars" trilogy, has died aged 85, his management company announced Sunday.

title: F1 driver Grosjean involved in horror crash during Bahrain GP
description: Formula One driver Romain Grosjean was involved in a horrific crash that left his car engulfed in flames at the Bahrain Grand Prix on Sunday, causing the race to be halted.

title: Car bomb kills at least 40 Afghan soldiers
description: A car bomb attack in Afghanistan's central province of Ghazni killed at least 40 Afghan soldiers and wounded 24, Ghazni public health department told CNN on Sunday.

title: Republican senator says he hopes Trump will attend inauguration
description: During an interview with CNN's Dana Bash, Sen. Roy Blunt (R-MO) said he hopes President Trump will attend the inauguration of President-elect Joe Biden.

title: Biden administration prepares to inherit controversial Trump immigration policies
description: When President-elect Joe Biden comes into office, he will inherit the Trump administration's restrictionist immigration agenda, which cut access to asylum and has kept migrants in limbo in Mexico while they await humanitarian protection in the US.

title: Opinion: Trump transition show is jumping the shark
description: If your grandparents or great-grandparents were living in Mississippi, Colorado or Texas in 1939 (like two of mine were), they may have celebrated Thanksgiving twice, thanks to Franklin D. Roosevelt's effort to bail out struggling retailers by moving Thanksgiving up a week -- thus extending the holiday shopping season.

title: Analysis: The worsening pandemic raises the stakes for Biden's economic program
description: Sitting in an Iowa diner a year ago, candidate Joe Biden aimed his economic agenda at the widening gap between America's rich and everyone else.

title: Denver Broncos have no quarterbacks for Saints game due to NFL Covid-19 protocols
description: The Denver Broncos have lost all of their quarterbacks for Sunday's game against the New Orleans Saints, after they were declared ineligible for play due to NFL Covid-19 protocols.

title: Mike Tyson's boxing comeback ends in draw

title: The mysterious silver monolith in the Utah desert has disappeared
description: A tall, silver, shining metal monolith discovered in the desert in southeastern Utah -- which prompted theories of alien placement and drew determined hikers to its secret location -- has now disappeared, the state's Bureau of Land Management said Saturday.

title: All Blacks great Dan Carter on the 'roller coaster of emotions' of his playing career and the importance of mental health

title: Secret warehouse parties get shut down
